instruction: List five ingredients for a vegetarian chili.
output:
- Tomatoes
- Red/Green peppers
- Onion
- Garlic
- Bell Pepper
- Beans (pinto, black, kidney, etc.)
- Chili powder
- Cumin
- Oregano
- Cayenne pepper 
- Vegetable stock
- Groundnut
- Corn
- Mushrooms
- Chipotle peppers 
- Coriander
- Avocado
- Lime juice
